{"tid":2378014,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"舊notebook想換電同火牛，請問有冇鋪頭推介？","createTime":"2021-01-24T06:09:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-24T09:30:25.000Z","uid":189277,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3ceaf684f76326608c5679a453a5df0bf9776675","tid":2378014,"uid":189277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T06:09:58.000Z","msg":"大學時期ownership programme買咗部ASUS notebook（型號R551L），其實到咁上下都開始壞，主要係叉唔到電，壞電池同火牛，早半年直情開唔到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n早排拎咗去原廠問，係佢個到插電竟然仲開到，但係型號太舊，原廠都冇零件整到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />原廠冇電換，買火牛要四舊水<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想問下咁多位巴絲有冇去開邊間鋪頭推介，可以搵到代用牛同換到電<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實部機仲用到，唔想就咁浪費咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔該哂咁多位先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1eec6ae63337220759b2addc62f184c61dec649","tid":2378014,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T06:12:40.000Z","msg":"高登囉2手果d鋪"},{"pid":"f1d49d4307cf7ea3449e04b1eee7a6245203a2bb","tid":2378014,"uid":189277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1eec6ae63337220759b2addc62f184c61dec649","tid":2378014,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T06:12:40.000Z","msg":"高登囉2手果d鋪"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T06:29:56.000Z","msg":"有冇話邊間推介/千祈唔好去？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n少行黃金高登驚俾人劏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3f86e6986053e0e47c1409913cb62447ade608d","tid":2378014,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1d49d4307cf7ea3449e04b1eee7a6245203a2bb","tid":2378014,"uid":189277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1eec6ae63337220759b2addc62f184c61dec649","tid":2378014,"uid":228143,"l